    |State Mgmt  |stateManagementIRP  | 28.626|

## Validating XML against the schemas
	1> rr("/usr/lib/erlang/lib/xmerl-*/include/*").
	2> {ok, State} = xmerl_xsd:process_schema("all.xsd").
	3> {XmlElement, _} = xmerl_scan:file("configData.xml").
	4> xmerl_xsd:validate(XmlElement, State).

